data.description: Welcome to 1105 Capstone Crossing, a beautiful fully updated 3-bedroom 2 bath home in ideal location of VB. This home boasts a large lot with fully fenced in backyard and spacious floor plan with countless updates. In December of 2022 the seller updated: new HVAC system, floors and paint throughout the home, removed the popcorn ceiling, two new vanities for both bathrooms, and a new refrigerator. The stone design in front of the fireplace has also been added along with replacing and painting the door frame on the backdoor. 3 military bases are 10 miles away or less and just minutes from beaches and Town Center. Must see in person to appreciate!
